17.10.0                                                               2017-10-10
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Add: module_xml_parser, complex function and larger (10*maxpath) strings.
- Update: Makefiles use of $(RM) and - to avoid errors with missing files.

17.12.0                                                               2017-12-22
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Update: Module names now end in '_bmod' to avoid conflicts with user modules.

17.12.1                                                               2017-12-31
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Add: modification_time() in module_compiler_dependant (from project VolFEM).
- Add: dimension 10*maxpath in module_xml_parser (from project VolFEM).
- Add: operator .IsNewerThan. in module_files (from project VolFEM).
- Update: changes in word_count and word (from project VolFEM).

18.01.0                                                               2018-01-09
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Update: FORD links of type [[module]] updated to the new ending '_bmod'.
- Update: FORD comments ended with two blank spaces when paragraph ends.

18.02.0                                                               2018-02-16
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Change: libraries are named without version, os or compiler.
- Change: include (.MOD) files are not distributed.

18.02.0                                                               2018-02-21
